---
title: Lime BBQ Chicken with Fresh Salsa
description: Pour the tequila and get ready for some sticky sweet lime and BBQ sauce-slathered chicken thighs! Fresh salsa and some crunchy tortilla chips round out this true Tex-Mex dinner!
